com.complexible.common.openrdf.query

Class AbstractBooleanQueryResultWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.openrdf.query.AbstractQueryResultWriter
      • com.complexible.common.openrdf.query.AbstractBooleanQueryResultWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BooleanQueryResultHandler, QueryResultHandler, BooleanQueryResultWriter, QueryResultWriter

    public abstract class AbstractBooleanQueryResultWriter
extends AbstractQueryResultWriter
implements BooleanQueryResultWriter

    BooleanQueryResultWriter base for creating custom writer implementations which throws UnsupportedOperationException exceptions for the non-boolean result format methods which are incorrectly in the QueryResultWriter interface.

    Since:
    1.0
